                        <li><strong>Restriction of Processing</strong><br>You have a right to require us to stop processing the personal information Myanmar ICT Solutions Limited holds about you other than for storage purposes in the following circumstances: (1) you believe the personal information is not accurate for the period it takes for us to verify whether the data is accurate; (2) Myanmar ICT Solutions Limited wishes to erase the personal information as the processing it is doing is unlawful, but you want Myanmar ICT Solutions Limited to simply restrict the use of that data; (3) Myanmar ICT Solutions Limited no longer needs the personal information for the purposes of the processing but you require it to retain the data for the establishment, exercise or defense of legal claims; or (4) you have objected to Myanmar ICT Solutions Limited processing personal information it holds about you on the basis of its legitimate interest and you wish it to stop processing the personal information while it determines whether there is an overriding interest in Myanmar ICT Solutions Limited retaining such information.</li>
